.TH VAULTOS-CONFIG-TUI 1 "2024-01-01" "VaultOS" "VaultOS Manual"
.SH NAME
vaultos-config-tui \- VaultOS configuration manager (TUI)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vaultos-config-tui
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vaultos-config-tui
is an interactive text-based configuration manager for VaultOS settings.
It provides an easy interface to configure window manager, themes, key bindings,
workspaces, and application launcher settings.
.SH FEATURES
.TP
Window Manager Settings
Configure window gaps, borders, layouts
.TP
Theme Configuration
Select and switch between themes
.TP
Key Bindings
View key binding information
.TP
Workspace Management
Configure workspace settings
.TP
Application Launcher
Set default application launcher
.TP
Status Bar
Configure status bar appearance
.SH CONFIGURATION FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/vaultos/config.json
Main configuration file (JSON format)
.TP
.I ~/.config/vaultwm/config
Window manager configuration (text format)
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vaultos-config-validator (1),
.BR vaultos-theme-switcher (1),
.BR vaultwm (1)
